Takt Time

Taktzeit - rhythmic time in German

Gives rhythm to the system to operate at a steady pace to meet customer demand.

Takt Time = Available Time / Customer Demand

Amount of time is should take to maintain flow.
If an operation takes longer than takt time then it will cause a bottleneck in the delivery of custoomer demand.
